"Creative vanguards SectionZ Records have added 2010 Juno Award Winners Me&John and Discovery Project and Light Up the Night Festival Winners City 17 to their already impressive list of EDM taste makers on their most recent monthly compilation, "Fresh Vol. 3" . Featuring the best and most innovative music, spanning Dubstep & Electro to Vocal Downtempo & Big Room Electro Trap (wut?), "Fresh Vol. 3" continues the boutique label's commitment to further push the boundaries of electronic music."


This curated release series collects the best and taste-making sounds we have heard over the last month from up and coming artists from all over the world. We chose this music because we believe they represent change in the face of formulaic EDM, some because of style, others because of attitude, but in the end they all represent the three pillars of what we look for in musicians.
